data.description: Welcome to this stunning 1.5 level house located at 325 Covenant Dr. This spacious property offers an impressive 3,184 square feet of living space, providing ample room for comfortable living. As you step inside, you'll immediately appreciate the large open floor plan that creates a seamless flow throughout the home. The inviting atmosphere is perfect for both relaxation and entertaining guests. With 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms on the main level, there's plenty of space for everyone to enjoy their own privacy. The second level holds the 3rd full bathroom, massive bonus room, and an additional multipurpose room with a walk in closet which can be utilized as an office, playroom, etc. to meet the needs of your family.  The master bedroom is a true retreat, featuring a double tray ceiling and a cozy sitting area where you can unwind after a long day. The luxurious en suite bathroom boasts double vanities, a jetted tub, a separate shower, and not one but two walk-in closets. The gourmet kitchen is every chef's dream, equipped with granite countertops, a convenient breakfast bar, a pantry, and ample storage space. It's the ideal setting for preparing delicious meals and creating lasting memories with family and friends. Step outside onto the covered patio and take in the picturesque views of the inground pool with a chlorine filter. This backyard oasis is perfect for hosting summer parties or simply relaxing under the sun. Recent upgrades including a new HVAC system, new ductwork, and replaced plumbing ensure that this home is not only beautiful but also functional and efficient. Situated on just over a half-acre lot, this property also features a gazebo, playground, dog lot, privacy fence, and underground utilities. You'll have everything you need to make this house your dream home. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity! Schedule your showing today and start envisioning your life in this wonderful property.
